name: CAT MOMENT
description:
Inspired by the cat woman character who is actually an anti-hero but has an extraordinary heart. Cat woman known as criminal who carry out many theft activities against the elite, but the result is not to work for herself but to help others.

This artwork also marks the phenomenon of the widespread presence of cats in real life with evidence that has spread on social media. Cats are beloved pets, because they are docile, funny, playful and friendly.

Cat Moment combines the two phenomena above with hope of becoming a reflective medium to keep doing good with anyone, anytime and in anyway. Hopefully we can be like a cat Moment that is not only present but also lives that should be lived.


----------------------------------------------------------

This is the second artwork from chapter 1 of my journey at nft. all works are done using digital painting without losing my style and soul which is usually present on canvas.

Thank you for appreciating my art.
If you have collected this artwork, don't forget to share it on your social media and tag me.

Best Regards,
Montha
